ceš me iseci?

438
00:37:41,525 --> 00:37:43,459
-Skoci!
-Sranje.

439
00:37:43,661 --> 00:37:46,129
Trebalo bi te biti sramota.

440
00:37:46,664 --> 00:37:48,757
Povuci nož na poluslepog starca.

441
00:37:48,933 --> 00:37:51,299
...i isterati ga napolje na kišu.

442
00:37:52,336 --> 00:37:55,999
U moje vreme skitnice su se
meðusobno poštovale.

443
00:37:58,309 --> 00:38:00,971
-Kako se zoveš?
- Frances.

444
00:38:01,145 --> 00:38:03,875
Mene zovu Blind Dog Fulton.

445
00:38:04,048 --> 00:38:06,312
Takoðe poznat kao Willie Brown.

446
00:38:06,484 --> 00:38:08,213
-Takoðe...
-A on?

447
00:38:08,386 --> 00:38:10,877
Lightning Boy Martone.
poznat kao Eugene.

448
00:38:11,055 --> 00:38:13,182
Lightning Boy i Blind Dog.

449
00:38:13,357 --> 00:38:15,222
Šta bi ste do kurca vi trebali biti?

450
00:38:15,393 --> 00:38:18,362
-Mi smo bluesmani
- Bar sam to ja.

451
00:38:18,529 --> 00:38:20,394
On je s Long Islanda.

452
00:38:20,564 --> 00:38:22,725
Skitamo okolo.
Šta je s tobom?

453
