467
00:39:02,840 --> 00:39:04,205
Ne.

468
00:39:04,375 --> 00:39:06,605
Pa, bio je više kao staracki dom.

469
00:39:08,145 --> 00:39:11,046
Staracki dom?
Dobra fora.

470
00:39:11,215 --> 00:39:13,843
Izvinite me dok obucem pantalone.

471
00:39:19,557 --> 00:39:21,047
Spremaj se.
-Šta?

472
00:39:21,225 --> 00:39:22,590
-Pakuj se.
-Zašto?

473
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:24,523
