Hajde, Willie, idemo u ambar 
da se odmorimo ok?

626
00:49:13,917 --> 00:49:16,943
Ne brini se, Lightning, necu se
 veceras srušiti mrtav.

627
00:49:17,621 --> 00:49:20,954
